    "Consequently, CodeS-15B emerges as the leading open-source pre-trained language model in SQL generation.",
    "Furthermore, smaller models exhibit a more pronounced improvement compared to larger models.",
    "This observation underscores our initial hypothesis that smaller models, due to their constrained parameters, may not be optimally trained for SQL-related tasks.",
